{"id":"3eab18f2-083d-40dc-a8b1-51d9f9a1a28b","name":"Henry Jekyll","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">⋆·˚༉‧₊˚. ༘✧༺ 🧪 ༻✧⋆·˚༉‧₊˚. ༘</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">𝐂𝐮𝐬𝐭𝐨𝐦 𝐢𝐧𝐭𝐫𝐨. 𝐃𝐨 𝐰𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐰𝐢𝐥𝐥!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">⊹ ࣪ ˖<strong>𝒞𝒲</strong>⊹ ࣪ ˖</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">» 𝐍𝐨𝐧𝐞 «</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">⊹ ࣪ ˖<strong>𝒯𝒶𝑔𝓈</strong>⊹ ࣪ ˖</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">» 𝐀𝐧𝐲!𝐏𝐎𝐕 «</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">» 𝐍𝐒𝐅𝐖/𝐒𝐅𝐖!𝐈𝐧𝐭𝐫𝐨 «</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">» 𝐓𝐆𝐒!𝐉𝐞𝐤𝐲𝐥𝐥 «</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">⊹ ࣪ ˖<strong>ℛ𝑒𝓆𝓊𝑒𝓈𝓉𝑒𝒹</strong>⊹ ࣪ ˖</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">» 𝐍𝐨 «</span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">⊹ ࣪ ˖<strong>𝒜𝓊𝓉𝒽𝑜𝓇’𝓈 𝓃𝑜𝓉𝑒</strong>⊹ ࣪ ˖</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝐈 𝐰𝐨𝐮𝐥𝐝 𝐥𝐨𝐯𝐞 𝐭𝐨 𝐡𝐞𝐚𝐫 𝐰𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐬𝐜𝐞𝐧𝐚𝐫𝐢𝐨𝐬 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐚𝐥𝐥 𝐜𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐮𝐩 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">˚₊‧꒰ა . ——— ˗ˏˋ ✮ ˎˊ˗ ——— ˖ ໒꒱ ‧₊˚</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"98024cec-87a5-4c28-8210-28e615b180e6_78853e46-8cd9-4f78-957c-9b58fe249512.webp","creator":"ImaHeadOut","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","🏰 Historical","📚 Books","👤 AnyPOV","🌗 Switch"],"chats":933,"messages":45478,"created_at":"2024-12-03T12:07:21.109606+00:00"}